commit message:
Support for Google Code Git repos

Can launch from Web urls, also incorporates patched version of JGit to deal
with http://code.google.com/p/support/issues/detail?id=5576

Be less annoying by only showing Agit intent when user hits 'Source'

ie https://code.google.com/p/test-for-agit/source/checkout

There are not yet many Google Code projects using Git, it's a bit over the
top showing the Agit intent for every single Google Project page.
